      <item>
        <title>Meeru for Mac</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;content__item-img-center animated zoomIn&quot; src=&quot;/Appolo-demo//images/meeru/meeru-1.png&quot; alt=&quot;Meeru for Mac&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;content__item-center&quot;&gt;
Meeru is the app that allows you to play multiple videos from streaming websites at the same time.
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;section_title&quot;&gt;Supported services&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;meeru_services&quot;&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&amp;#xe80c;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li&gt;&amp;#xe80d;&lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;li class=&quot;ted&quot;&gt;TED&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;video-container&quot;&gt;&lt;iframe width=&quot;80%&quot; max-width=&quot;640px&quot; height=&quot;315&quot; src=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/embed/tQzKfvn3RZY &quot; frameborder=&quot;0&quot; allowfullscreen=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;section_title&quot;&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;meeru_features&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;Play up to 10 videos at the same time.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Add and remove videos without hassle.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Move position of a video simply by dragging it around.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Save the video lists to a .meeru file. Simply double click the .meeru file to re-open all the saved videos.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;section_title&quot;&gt;Download&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;content__item-img-center animated zoomIn&quot; src=&quot;/Appolo-demo//images/app_store_coming_soon.png&quot; alt=&quot;Coming Soon&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
